## Overview

Complete the image feature by adding essential controls: resize handles, alt text editor (accessibility), and delete button. This makes the image feature fully usable and accessible.

**Context:** Phase 1-3 shipped core upload functionality (drag-drop, paste, IndexedDB storage). Phase 4 adds UI controls to make images truly usable.

**Impact:**
- **User Value:** CRITICAL - Without resize/delete, images are hard to manage
- **Accessibility:** Alt text is WCAG AA requirement
- **Marketing:** Completes "Images in Notes" feature (100% not 75%)
