## Problem Statement

**Current State:**
- ✅ Users can upload images (button, drag-drop, paste)
- ✅ Images compress and store in IndexedDB
- ✅ Images render with blob URLs
- ❌ **NO resize controls** (images always full width - not ideal)
- ❌ **NO alt text** (accessibility violation - WCAG AA)
- ❌ **NO delete button** (must delete entire note to remove image)

**User Pain:**
- Cannot resize images to fit content (huge screenshots dominate note)
- Cannot add alt text (screen reader users can't understand images)
- Cannot delete mistakenly uploaded images (except by deleting note)

**Competitive Gap:**
- Obsidian: Resize with drag handles, alt text, delete menu
- Notion: Resize with handles, alt text, easy delete
- Neuman Brain: ❌ NO CONTROLS (incomplete feature)

